/>\n點會影響執法<br />\n<br />\n行得正企得正，跟規矩驚條毛，除非<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7144e8d6739babf6fefe9029b48c5f0f7a2dd1fd","tid":1404550,"uid":17399,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-04T05:34:17.000Z","msg":"快啦屌"},{"pid":"be2c99bbd08d695e353e23d7146a50d3100a9d1b","tid":1404550,"uid":69899,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-04T05:34:20.000Z","msg":"講撚左成個月<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/z.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"327e07d9722caa5034310515de669f318bfdedf5","tid":1404550,"uid":266503,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-04T05:35:20.000Z","msg":"政權除了要我們恐懼多，還要散佈仇恨。<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.inmediahk.net/node/1065677\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.inmediahk.net%2Fnode%2F1065677&d=Yc7MVk%2FjSym3Ma7OIK9USObr9%2BGymSeLOXabm6KdyvY%3D&h=a81b8a3a\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.inmediahk.net%2Fnode%2F1065677&h=892f01aa\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.inmediahk.net/node/1065677</a><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n「人民不應該害怕他們的政府，政府應該害怕它的人民。」（People should not be afraid of their governments. Governments should be afraid of their people.）<br />\n<br />\n「藝術家用謊言揭露真相，政治家用謊言掩蓋真相。」（Artists use lies to tell the truth, while politicians use them to cover the truth up.）<br />\n<br />\n「沒有舞蹈的革命，是不值得發動的革命。」（A revolution without dancing is a revolution not worth having）<br />\n<br />\n「面具之下只是個血肉之軀，而在這面具之下的，還有一個理念，只不過，理念，是刀槍不入的。」（Beneath this mask there is more than flesh. Beneath this mask there is an idea, Mr.Creedy, and ideas are bulletproof..）<br />\n<br />\n「我們的尊嚴可能不值錢，但它卻是我們唯一真正擁有的東西。它是我們最後一寸領地，但在那一寸領地裡，我們是自由的。」（Our integrity sells for so little, but it is all we really have. It is the very last inch of us, but within that inch, we are free）<br />\n<br />\n「力量來自團結，團結來自信念」（Strength through unity, unity through faith）<br />\n<br />\n「恐懼往往是政府的終極武器。」（Fear became the ultimate tool of this government）<br />\n<br />\n「就算政府擁有的武力統治不讓人民發言，自由的言論仍然充滿著強大的力量。」（the truncheon may be used in lieu of conversation, words will always retain their power)"},{"pid":"3a28863c2835eb7c347b989210b3691c7046e962","tid":1404550,"uid":98431,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-04T05:35:29.000Z","msg":"兩個月 對家都進化左<br />\n<br />\n尋日班黑衫黑鬼已經一步一步浮底加印證<br />\n<br />\n仲有好多貼證扮自己人 引人衝呢到 圍果到 塞車廠之類<br />\n<br />\n抽返身出黎 諗下721 728 同尋晚點死<br />\n<br />\n就唔難明點解去到呢一刻仲會有假手足叫人上"},{"pid":"5f2117f43505a861f813e51c4b683c46b669625a","tid":1404550,"uid":224402,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-04T05:35:42.000Z","msg":"叫佢上訪啦 垃圾禮義廉"},{"pid":"73f9cd9b29f9def1778194d4dbfaaf824827cf43","tid":1404550,"uid":25434,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-04T05:35:58.000Z","msg":"還我解放軍<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ab24d8a5cd94beda1c4ed3dabc38b58419d9dc51","tid":1404550,"uid":108946,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-04T05:37:02.000Z","msg":"我而家已經相信"},{"pid":"c09db6e87bd37b92a5da0ee6e2036eaea89a90d3","tid":1404550,"uid":149003,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-04T05:37:06.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/4vVzCty.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F4vVzCty.gif&h=30110c3c&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n係就快<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8522057737a290ac40334eb363b7196da02fd83c","tid":1404550,"uid":51583,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-04T05:37:40.000Z","msg":"到時香港真正癱瘓"},{"pid":"fc755969e856bcfac1c93eb7df01f8dbc43098e1","tid":1404550,"uid":136696,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-04T05:38:09.000Z","msg":"希望解放軍可以主持公道！"},{"pid":"868c9ac097ea4de8c728f3d94d1f317d3808da06",